  "reference_number": "RUS2748",
  "remarks": "\nROSNEFT MARINE (UK) LIMITED is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the grounds that it is involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia, as it is associated to PJSC Rosneft, which is an entity involved in a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, namely, the Russian energy sector. \n",
